How to Install
	1) Copy src/phpSecurityClass.php file on your website

	2) Add class after `<body>`:
	<?php 
	     include("phpSecurityClass.php"); 
	     $security = new phpSecurityClass();
	?>
	
	2) Use one of class function:
	<?php
		if($security->name("John Titor")){
			echo "Correct Input";
		}else{
			echo "Error";
		}
	?>


